<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RM 风险管理系统</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif;background:#f7f4ef;padding:2rem}
.container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;padding:2rem;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
h1{color:#2d2d2d;margin-bottom:.5rem;font-size:1.8rem}
.subtitle{color:#6b8e9f;font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:2rem}
.summary{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem}
.summary-card{background:#f9f9f9;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:6px;border-top:3px solid #6b8e9f}
.summary-card.highlight{border-top-color:#c9a227}
.summary-label{font-size:.85rem;color:#666;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.summary-value{font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#2d2d2d}
.summary-sub{font-size:.8rem;color:#999;margin-top:.3rem}
.section{margin-top:2rem}
.section-title{font-size:1.2rem;color:#2d2d2d;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #c9a227;padding-left:1rem}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
th,td{padding:.75rem;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0}
th{background:#6b8e9f;color:#fff;font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem}
td{font-size:.85rem;color:#2d2d2d}
.status-dot{display:inline-block;width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;margin-right:.5rem}
.status-dot.green{background:#28a745}
.status-dot.yellow{background:#ffc107}
.status-dot.red{background:#dc3545}
.chart-area{background:#f9f9f9;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:6px;margin-top:1rem;text-align:center;color:#999}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h1>RM 风险管理系统</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">全业务风险预估 · 财报支撑 · 审计合规</p>

  <div class="summary">
    <div class="summary-card highlight">
      <div class="summary-label">总在贷余额</div>
      <div class="summary-value">500 亿</div>
      <div class="summary-sub">7 条业务线</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="summary-label">加权终损率</div>
      <div class="summary-value">5.8%</div>
      <div class="summary-sub">vs 上月 -0.2pp</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="summary-label">拨备计提</div>
      <div class="summary-value">29.3 亿</div>
      <div class="summary-sub">拨备覆盖率 120%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="summary-label">预警业务线</div>
      <div class="summary-value">1</div>
      <div class="summary-sub">小微贷款观察中</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">业务线风险概览</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>业务线</th>
          <th>在贷余额（亿）</th>
          <th>客户数（万）</th>
          <th>预估终损率</th>
          <th>拨备计提（亿）</th>
          <th>MoM 变化</th>
          <th>状态</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>菲律宾现金贷</strong></td>
          <td>85</td>
          <td>42.5</td>
          <td>8.5%</td>
          <td>7.2</td>
          <td style="color:#28a745">-0.3pp</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>国内消费贷</strong></td>
          <td>180</td>
          <td>125.8</td>
          <td>4.2%</td>
          <td>7.6</td>
          <td style="color:#28a745">-0.1pp</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>小微贷款</strong></td>
          <td>120</td>
          <td>18.3</td>
          <td>6.8%</td>
          <td>8.2</td>
          <td style="color:#dc3545">+0.5pp</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot yellow"></span>观察</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>信用卡分期</strong></td>
          <td>65</td>
          <td>85.2</td>
          <td>3.5%</td>
          <td>2.3</td>
          <td style="color:#999">持平</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>汽车金融</strong></td>
          <td>30</td>
          <td>5.6</td>
          <td>2.8%</td>
          <td>0.8</td>
          <td style="color:#28a745">-0.2pp</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>教育分期</strong></td>
          <td>12</td>
          <td>8.9</td>
          <td>4.5%</td>
          <td>0.5</td>
          <td style="color:#999">持平</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>其他业务</strong></td>
          <td>8</td>
          <td>3.2</td>
          <td>5.2%</td>
          <td>0.4</td>
          <td style="color:#28a745">-0.1pp</td>
          <td><span class="status-dot green"></span>正常</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Vintage 曲线（菲律宾现金贷）</h2>
    <div class="chart-area">
      [Vintage 曲线图表]<br>
      展示各月份 Cohort 的逾期率演化趋势<br>
      预估 M12 终损率: 8.5%
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">拨备计提趋势</h2>
    <div class="chart-area">
      [拨备计提趋势图]<br>
      2024 Q1-Q4 及 2025 Q1 拨备计提金额与覆盖率<br>
      当前拨备覆盖率: 120%（监管要求 ≥100%）
    </div>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top:2rem;color:#999;font-size:.8rem;text-align:center">
    * 所有数据已脱敏处理，仅用于展示 | 更新时间: 2025-02-16
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
